{"type": "article", "id": 14053, "title": "鸡蛋地图", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-27T07:48:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143511LA6VjWMPqc1UJ7sR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t匈牙利设计师 dénes sátor 的“鸡蛋地图”专为那些无暇打开地图以及寻找 WiFi 困难的游客。它由弹性很好的橡胶做成，里面填充着空气。无论是捏在手里，放在口袋里，还是在空中抛来抛去都无需担心。地图上街道都是白色的，不同街区以颜色的深浅来区分，还附上了各种小图标。使用时只要将“鸡蛋”捏在手中，放大目的地，就能探到想去的地方。前提是，你要会看地图。<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/egg-map-denes-sator-08-25-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看相关信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416588fTBpb3r0eNYGvJn.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"495\" title=\"4\" alt=\"4\" data-ratio=\"0.60513447\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416588wQKB5mUvJaexiLO.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"578\" title=\"4\" alt=\"4\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141659OBqiusRQfNpa1DUr.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"578\" title=\"4\" alt=\"4\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141659lA1srC3xXbhn8YzD.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"485\" title=\"4\" alt=\"4\" data-ratio=\"0.59290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}